                          <note>Quire descriptions: quires 1–4, 6–7 balanced; quire 8 adjusted balanced; quire 5 unbalanced. Navigation systems: 1) brown yarn sewn into corners of <locus target="#i #ii #43 #44 #45 #74" facs="001 002 045 046 076"/> to mark the location of miniatures.</note>
